                            <comment id="15305993" author="thetaphi" created="Sun, 29 May 2016 17:04:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Happens for me, too, on every JVM version.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;FYI, I implemented something similar for the extraction module or also for the SystemInfoHandler: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/lucene-solr/blob/5e5fd662575105de88d8514b426bccdcb4c76948/solr/core/src/java/org/apache/solr/handler/admin/SystemInfoHandler.java#L214-L232&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/lucene-solr/blob/5e5fd662575105de88d8514b426bccdcb4c76948/solr/core/src/java/org/apache/solr/handler/admin/SystemInfoHandler.java#L214-L232&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It uses the java.beans.Introspector class to introspect beans and read/set properties. This should be preferred, if you need to guess method names (setProperty, getProperty and isProperty for booleans).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think the same should be done for the plugin utils, if they use bean properties.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
